Quickstrike:



Quickstrike glowered. He was at where Black Arachnia said he should 
go, but no one greeted him. He sensed other Predacons there. He took 
a step back from the ramp and looked up.

"Black Arachnia sent me," he said, hoping someone would hear 
him. "Now what?"
